Package: jobber
Version: 0.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: docker.io (>= 20.10), docker-compose-plugin (>= 2.0)
Recommends: nvidia-container-toolkit
Maintainer: distance1186 <distance1186@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/distance1186/jobber
Description: Self-hosted job aggregation and tracking system
 Jobber is a self-hosted job aggregation and tracking system powered by a
 local LLM agent. It scrapes job boards, classifies listings using AI, and
 provides a web dashboard for tracking applications.
 .
 This package installs the jobber-setup CLI and project files. After
 installation, run 'jobber-setup install' to complete the guided setup.
